      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ILLUMINATOR (3) brought up his 7th career win last start at this track (30.18). Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Hard to go past. PAW IMPERIAL (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (29.95) at Sandown in a Grade 5. Can find the frame this time. REUBEN HILL (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (31.04) at Ballarat behind Overland Boy in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expected to be in this for a long way. AUNTY FAYE (4) can run a bold race on best form.",
